  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ligo is an adventure Sokoban game, where you solve handcrafted puzzles and mysteries about the world by merging, cutting, pushing smalls creatures together and crushing squids with blocks.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/7a3da0501506e6e10e466dabdd312d1e.poster.avif?t=1758293032\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/7a3da0501506e6e10e466dabdd312d1e.webm?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/7a3da0501506e6e10e466dabdd312d1e.mp4?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each part of the world has different rules and challenges. Explore an interconnected world of puzzles and mysteries. You take control of small blob-like creature and make them work together to solve many types of challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/d958712a2e3bcce2d88d20a930d1d6e1.poster.avif?t=1758293032\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/d958712a2e3bcce2d88d20a930d1d6e1.webm?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/d958712a2e3bcce2d88d20a930d1d6e1.mp4?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/ea0f4592220315b7f5539f85976c4dd7.poster.avif?t=1758293032\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/ea0f4592220315b7f5539f85976c4dd7.webm?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/ea0f4592220315b7f5539f85976c4dd7.mp4?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features :</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nonlinear puzzle game </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Challenging and rewarding </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More than 200+ handcrafted puzzles </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Full of mysteries and secrets </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/113dd0d63ecc7056c8e5f879e0031254.poster.avif?t=1758293032\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/113dd0d63ecc7056c8e5f879e0031254.webm?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2462810/extras/113dd0d63ecc7056c8e5f879e0031254.mp4?t=1758293032\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
